            <div id="faq_11" class="card-content" style="display: none;">
                <div class="content">
                    <p>We really hope you don’t experience any issues with your prize, however, if there is any problem with the prize, please let us know via our contact page and we will do everything we can to solve the problem quickly.</p>
                    <p>We will review on a case by case basis, and will do everything in our power to get it fixed, offer a cash alternative or replace the broken item. This might not always be the case and we ask that you work with us so we can resolve it as soon as possible.</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
